==English==

===Etymology===
From the [[Latin]] word for "broken"

===Pronunciation===
* SAMPA: /'br\EttSA:/

===Noun===
'''breccia'''

# Breccia is typically a [[rock]] composed of angular fragments in a [[matrix]] that may be of a similar or a different material.

